# RUNBOOK — Provider Federation Activation

This runbook tells you exactly **what to set**, **when to set it**, and **how to verify**.

---

## Phases

### Phase 0 — Default (MVP+)
- Keep federation **disabled** (default).
- Providers manage billing directly in each client instance.

